WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.666 --> 00:00:03.933
What’s with the panic?

2
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:05.666
Your Highness.

3
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:07.300
Please come with me quickly.

4
00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.100
What happened? What’s going on?

5
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:09.900
Oh no.

6
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.000
Your Highness, there’s no time to explain.

7
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.066
The Emperor is still out in the rear garden in the cold.

8
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:18.666
No matter how anyone tries to persuade him,

9
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:20.500
the Emperor won’t listen.

10
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:24.500
It’s late, and I didn’t dare to disturb the Empress Dowager.

11
00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:27.500
Shen Wu had me come to fetch you.

12
00:00:27.533 --> 00:00:30.200
He said you would know what to do.

13
00:00:30.966 --> 00:00:32.233
Hurry, let’s go.

14
00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.000
It’s really laughable, truly laughable.

15
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:43.666
The Emperor has been sitting there since the afternoon.

16
00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:45.433
He ordered everyone to stay away.

17
00:00:45.933 --> 00:00:48.366
He said he wanted to be alone.

18
00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:57.366
Your Majesty, what’s wrong?

19
00:00:57.366 --> 00:00:58.866
Please come back to the palace with me.

20
00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:09.500
No one is allowed near me.

21
00:01:09.966 --> 00:01:12.700
Your Majesty, it’s me, Song Qianyu.

22
00:01:18.066 --> 00:01:19.166
Why are you here?

23
00:01:23.900 --> 00:01:26.300
I’m sorry. I shouldn’t have treated you like that.

24
00:01:26.666 --> 00:01:27.833
I really am at fault.

25
00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:32.766
I’m sorry. I’m sorry to the Empress.

26
00:01:33.300 --> 00:01:35.066
Your Majesty, please come back to the palace with me.

27
00:01:38.566 --> 00:01:39.400
Alright.

28
00:01:45.533 --> 00:01:47.700
Your Majesty.

29
00:01:48.133 --> 00:01:49.900
Your Majesty, Your Majesty.
